^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Okay, time to start. Since we have such a large crowd, suggest we keep public chat to a minimum. The idea behind this lesson is to teach the basics behind all bidding systems. What I find with many players is they know all the complicated rules of bidding. I truly believe if you understand the concepts, you don't need to memorize nearly as many rules. So, what I am going to try to do is teach you the concepts.|
