Remember, South voluntarily went past 2 diamonds so it is a reverse. Now just to make it clear a reverse unfortunately is not completely precise. It does show at least a medium hand but you can also reverse with a maximum hand. So, in terms of points, you know opener has a minimum of 16 or so, but you are not sure what the maximum opener has. Opener's hand can either be medium or maximum.
 
