So, as responder, if you make any bid but 4sf or a game bid, you are not forcing to game. You are turning the captaincy back to opener. with a maximum, opener is responsible for bidding game. That is why reverses are difficult auctions. However, my other rule is "if you are not sure if a bid is forcing, assume it is." Therefore, if you are not sure whether or not to bid game, bid it. In the long run you will come out ahead.|
